Package: Rlab4
Type: Package
Title: Linear Regression Modelling
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Maria Treesa(marse306), Brian Masinde(brima748), Omkar
Maintainer: The package maintainer <mariatreesaa@gmail.com>
Description: Linear regression modelling using two approaches; Ordinary Least Squares
    and QR decomposition. The function linreg gives executes the former giving 
    t-values and p-values in addition to the estimates of beta. The function linreg_QR
    executes the latter of the approaches to get estimates of beta and Variance of beta.
